        {
            "title": "荷莫茲海峽長期封鎖加劇歐元區衰退風險",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"410\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/ONI_MeQ.yrRSQHgUTO0dDw--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTYwNg--/https://i-invdn-com.investing.com/news/LYNXMPEE0B0IE_M.jpg\" width=\"650\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">Investing.com - 荷莫茲海峽的持續封鎖正將歐元區推向衰退,能源成本上升、供應鏈中斷以及全球需求疲軟,都對這個在衝突爆發前就已經脆弱的經濟體造成壓力。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">戰爭進入第八週,BCA估計,在考慮管道改道和戰略儲備釋放後,全球石油市場面臨每日900萬至950萬桶的供應缺口——約佔全球消費量的10%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">到目前為止,市場基本上忽視了這場危機。歐洲股市自3月低點反彈7.8%,歐元兌美元收復失地,美國股市更攀升至歷史新高。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-dd540130-0511-3ebb-86f7-8041bce3db7b-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">BCA策略師Jeremie Peloso領導的團隊在報告中表示:「只有債券市場的表現與事實相符,即儘管有停火協議和反覆談判,荷莫茲海峽仍處於封鎖狀態。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">BCA指出,即使美國和伊朗逐步重新開放海峽,油輪在恢復通行後也需要四至六週才能抵達歐洲和亞洲,這意味著淨供應損失將達到2.5億至4億桶。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">策略師表示,全球可見庫存將觸及歷史低點,投資者的注意力將從油價轉向實物交付問題。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">歐洲對荷莫茲海峽運輸的依賴程度低於亞洲經濟體,但其疲弱的起始狀況使其特別容易受到衝擊。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">BCA寫道:「起點要低得多。一方面,這降低了持續通脹螺旋的可能性,但另一方面,這意味著相對較小的經濟痛苦就可能引發衰退。」策略師表示,預計歐洲央行將因此維持利率不變。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在評論前瞻性指標時,BCA強調,4月份快閃PMI數據顯示供應商交付時間急劇惡化,呼應了新冠疫情初期的模式。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">策略師指出,自本世紀初以來,每次重大供應衝擊都在12個月內導致經濟活動出現顯著收縮。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">對於投資者,該團隊建議增加對歷史上在石油供應衝擊後表現優異的板塊的投資——能源、製藥和公用事業。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">策略師表示:「反彈行情的時間已所剩無幾。市場將繼續上漲幾週,然後會出現更多證據顯示全球經濟正在停滯。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><em>此文章由人工智能協助翻譯。更多資訊，請參閱我們的使用條款。</em></p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E8%8D%B7%E8%8E%AB%E8%8C%B2%E6%B5%B7%E5%B3%BD%E9%95%B7%E6%9C%9F%E5%B0%81%E9%8E%96%E5%8A%A0%E5%8A%87%E6%AD%90%E5%85%83%E5%8D%80%E8%A1%B0%E9%80%80%E9%A2%A8%E9%9A%AA-143901816.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-05-02 22:58:48",
